rows.label: tlk41100121_01_msg0002
rows.name:
The monsters outside really,
really like shiny things!

rows.label: tlk41100121_01_msg0003
rows.name:
That's why they drop
money when you beat 'em!

rows.label: tlk41100121_01_msg0004
rows.name:
*sigh*... But knowing stuff
like that isn't gonna help
me learn how to swim.

rows.label: tlk41100121_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Even if I'm good at studying,
if I can't swim, I'm a failure
as a Gulan kid...
